56
00:05:01,502 --> 00:05:02,706
You're the iceman.

57
00:05:02,736 --> 00:05:03,774
Why is that?

58
00:05:03,804 --> 00:05:07,974
Because you're so cool.

59
00:05:10,711 --> 00:05:13,680
Hey, cher. Comment ça va?

60
