or next week to save.

75
00:05:45,112 --> 00:05:47,451
That's a big break for him.
That's too soon.

76
00:05:47,481 --> 00:05:48,685
We got a deal.

77
00:05:48,715 --> 00:05:51,251
You can't go on
without a lead singer.

78
00:05:52,152 --> 00:05:53,891
Already got a replacement.

79
00:05:53,921 --> 00:05:55,755
Really? Who?

80
00:05:57,658 --> 00:05:59,062
Billy Dupre.

81
00:05:59,092 --> 00:06:01,565
-Is you a fool?
-He sounds colored.

82
00:06:01,595 --> 00:06:02,733
This ain't radio.

83
00:06:02,763 --> 00:06:04,835
I ain't never had a white man
in here before.

84
00:06:04,865 --> 00:06:07,171
Oh, come on, Ruby.
Don't nobody mind

85
00:06:07,201 --> 00:06:09,006
