86
00:06:09,036 --> 00:06:11,041
-You is a fool.
- You know what, anyway,

87
00:06:11,071 --> 00:06:13,277
you got a full house
coming tonight. Uh-hmm.

88
00:06:13,307 --> 00:06:15,145
You know that Fridays are big.

89
00:06:15,175 --> 00:06:16,580
That's him out there?
He out there?

90
00:06:16,610 --> 00:06:18,178
Yeah, he out there.

91
00:06:18,846 --> 00:06:22,219
