up front or no go.

92
00:06:22,249 --> 00:06:26,419
Up front or no go? Jeez.

93
00:06:26,753 --> 00:06:29,155
Hold on. Let me light
that for you, Ruby.

94
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:35,065
What's your problem?

95
