Okay.
You got my word on it.

101
00:06:47,174 --> 00:06:48,378
You can't give
your word for him.

102
00:06:48,408 --> 00:06:49,580
It don't work like that.

103
00:06:49,610 --> 00:06:51,281
Now, now, Ruby,
come on please.

104
00:06:51,311 --> 00:06:52,482
Look, pay the man up front.

105
00:06:52,512 --> 00:06:54,651
I do it for him
then they all hit on me

106
00:06:54,681 --> 00:06:56,119
every week
for the same thing.

107
00:06:56,149 --> 00:06:57,550
No.

108
00:06:57,985 --> 00:06:59,723
-All right then.
- No, Billy, wait.

109
00:06:59,753 --> 00:07:01,492
Come on. Ruby, look,
I made the rounds.

110
00:07:01,522 --> 00:07:03,427
-I can't find nobody else.
- Look,

111
00:07:03,457 --> 00:07:05,058
just give me my cut.

112
00:07:05,225 --> 00:07:07,364
I won't tell anybody
I got it early.

113
00:07:07,394 --> 00:07:09,132
Hey. I won't say a word.

114
00:07:09,162 --> 00:07:12,298
You got my word on that.
You know I'm good for it.

115
00:07:15,102 --> 00:07:16,770
What is your trouble?

116
00:07:17,371 --> 00:07:19,042
That's none of your business.

117
00:07:19,072 --> 00:07:20,944
It's my business
if you don't show.

118
00:07:20,974 --> 00:07:22,542
I'll show up.

119
00:07:22,843 --> 00:07:25,245
Since when crackers
don't lie to niggas.

120
00:07:25,412 --> 00:07:27,447
I'm not going for that
Ms. Ruby.

121
00:07:27,681 --> 00:07:30,717
Don't you call me miss.
I'm a married woman.

122
00:07:37,024 --> 00:07:38,462
Give me your driver's license.

123
00:07:38,492 --> 00:07:41,365
Ruby, don't take that.
How's the man supposed to drive?

124
00:07:41,395 --> 00:07:43,096
Very carefully.

125
00:07:43,497 --> 00:07:45,865
Hand it over
if you want a deal.

126
00:07:52,205 --> 00:07:55,008
Well, you look more human
if you smile.

127
00:07:56,176 --> 00:07:57,677
Smile.

128
00:08:01,582 --> 00:08:02,982
Now you don't show.

129
00:08:03,917 --> 00:08:05,622
I'll come find you.

130
00:08:05,652 --> 00:08:07,153
Hey, Earl.

131
00:08:07,421 --> 00:08:09,359
Yeah, well,
as long as you understand.

132
00:08:09,389 --> 00:08:10,994
It's just a one-shot deal.

133
00:08:11,024 --> 00:08:12,592
One shot deal.

134
00:08:13,827 --> 00:08:15,933
Dress nice before you
come back here.

135
00:08:15,963 --> 00:08:17,534
What's the matter
with you, man?

136
00:08:17,564 --> 00:08:19,532
- He will.
- Thanks.

137
00:08:21,034 --> 00:08:23,573
Shit. What was I gonna do?

138
00:08:23,603 --> 00:08:25,305
Can he sing?

139
00:08:25,839 --> 00:08:27,540
Johnny says.

140
00:08:41,621 --> 00:08:43,356
Too damn hot.

141
00:08:44,324 --> 00:08:47,427
