to New Orleans

193
00:12:30,884 --> 00:12:33,190
to record a record
and become famous.

194
00:12:33,220 --> 00:12:35,258
And to take his place
for the next few nights,

195
00:12:35,288 --> 00:12:37,390
we have the one and only...

196
00:12:37,991 --> 00:12:39,692
Billy Dupre.

197
