Give me a cigarette.

198
00:15:16,983 --> 00:15:18,355
Man, that was great.

199
00:15:18,385 --> 00:15:20,152
It sure was.

200
00:15:34,401 --> 00:15:36,502
Hey there, good looking.

201
00:15:38,972 --> 00:15:42,141
You know the old songs too,
huh, Dupre?

202
00:15:43,276 --> 00:15:46,112
You're a pretty woman,
Mrs. Delacroix.

203
00:15:46,679 --> 00:15:49,849
